{'category': 'Notice', 'content': '<tbody> \n <tr> \n  <td class="nhangjv" id="zoom" valign="top" td><br> \n   <div id="BodyLabel">\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal" align="center"><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">四川大学自力志东奖学金评选通知</font></span></b></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 21pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">为推动四川大学教育事业发展，鼓励四川大学优秀大学生努力学习、为社会多做贡献，我校校友</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">四川省中国青年旅行社美途分社董事长刘自力先生</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">、</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">广东雅思教育管理有限公司朱志东先生特于四川大学计算机学院（软件学院）设立</font>“<font face="宋体">四川大学自力志东奖学金</font><font face="Arial">”</font><font face="宋体">，现将</font><font face="Arial">2016</font><font face="宋体">年</font><font face="Arial">“</font><font face="宋体">四川大学自力志东奖学金</font><font face="Arial">”</font><font face="宋体">评选有关事项细则如下：</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <!--?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /-->\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">一、</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="宋体">奖学金评选范围及评选名额</font></span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">“<font face="宋体">四川大学自力志东奖学金</font><font face="Arial">”</font><font face="宋体">用于奖励四川大学计算机学院（软件学院）的大二年级以上在读本科学生，</font><font face="Arial">2016</font><font face="宋体">年共计</font><font face="Arial">12</font><font face="宋体">名</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 18pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1" class="15"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">1、<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">综合奖学金：评选</font>2<font face="宋体">人，</font><font face="Arial">5000/</font><font face="宋体">人，计算机学院、软件学院各</font><font face="Arial">1</font><font face="宋体">人</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 18pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1" class="15"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">2、<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">单项奖学金</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">：评选</font>10<font face="宋体">人，</font><font face="Arial">2000/</font><font face="宋体">人，计算机学院、软件学院各</font><font face="Arial">5</font><font face="宋体">人</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">二、</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="宋体">奖学金评选条件</font></span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">“<font face="宋体">四川大学自力志东奖学金</font><font face="Arial">”</font><font face="宋体">旨在表彰奖励学业优异、品质优秀、专业能力突出</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">、综合素质高</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">的优秀在校本科生。申请者须具备以下条件：</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 18pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo2" class="15"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">1、<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">申请人需为计算机学院（软件学院）本科在读学生。原则上获得国家奖学金</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">和国家励志奖学金</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">以及获得</font>5000<font face="宋体">元以上社会奖助学金的同学不再参评本奖学金。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">2<font face="宋体">、思想政治素质高，得才兼备、勤奋学习的优秀学生</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">，</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">在校期间无任何违规违纪记录。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">3</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">、</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">学风严谨，善于思考，具有一定学术能力、特别是具有解决问题能力的优秀学生，或是学业成绩在专业、年级名列前茅的优秀者。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">4<font face="宋体">、注重学习，理论联系实践，善于解决实际问题，并取得优异成绩者。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 18pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 0.0000; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo3" class="15"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><span style="mso-list: Ignore">5、<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">有志于从事计算机、软件专业研究和工作的学生。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">6<font face="宋体">、</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">综合奖学金需在全年级综合排名前</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">20%<font face="宋体">。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">7</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">、</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">单项奖学金</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">：</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">奖励在</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">ACM<font face="宋体">、</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">大创</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><font face="宋体">、数学建模、微软创新杯、信息安全竞赛等相关高水平竞赛中获奖同学；奖励在校期间承担重大科研项目的同学；奖励在校企合作过程中，有重大研究成果的同学；奖励在创新创业实践中，有突出贡献的同学。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">8<font face="宋体">、同等条件下，家庭经济困难的学生优先。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">三、</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="宋体">奖学金评选原则</font></span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">1<font face="宋体">、坚持公平、公开、公正的方式作为推荐和评选的原则。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">2<font face="宋体">、评选中严格掌握评选条件、严格执行遴选程序。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">3<font face="宋体">、除申请人学业成绩优异外，还需特别注重个人品德，积极参加社会公益活动，以促进心系祖国，服务社会。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">四、</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="宋体">奖学金评选办法</font></span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">计算机学院（软件学院）组织成立</font>“<font face="宋体">四川大学自力志东奖学金</font><font face="Arial">”</font><font face="宋体">评审委员会（简称</font><font face="Arial">“</font><font face="宋体">评审会</font><font face="Arial">”</font><font face="宋体">）进行奖学金的评审工作并负责奖学金的管理及监督工作。具体评选办法如下：</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">1<font face="宋体">、评委会拟定评选通知并在基金会网站及学院网站公布。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">2<font face="宋体">、学生自己提出申请，经班级民主评议，学院学生科审议同意后，报评审会审核。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">3<font face="宋体">、评审会依据评选条件审核确定初选学生，公示无异议后，确定初步获奖者名单，并将相关材料报送备案。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">4<font face="宋体">、学院组织专家评审组对各奖项同学进行答辩考核，最后确定获得奖励的学生名单。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">5<font face="宋体">、公示：经专家评审组考核后，公示</font><font face="Arial">3</font><font face="宋体">天。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">6<font face="宋体">、公示无异议后，一次性发放奖学金，并对相关资料存档备案。</font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" class="MsoNormal"><b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; FONT-WEIGHT: bold; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">五、</font>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="宋体">奖学金申请程序</font></span></b><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">申请学生自行下载并填写《四川大学自力志东奖学金申请表》（见附件），并于</font>2016<font face="宋体">年</font><font face="Arial">11</font><font face="宋体">月</font><font face="Arial">28</font><font face="宋体">日前将《四川大学自力志东奖学金申请表》以及获奖情况证明、论文复印件、贫困证明等相关证明材料交到四川大学计算机学院（软件学院）学生科。请严格按照时间点报送，逾期视为自动放弃申请。</font></span></p>\n    <p style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 14.25pt; TEXT-INDENT: 18pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0000" class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt"><font face="宋体">附件：<a href="http://cs.scu.edu.cn/cs/rootfiles/2016/11/22/1478149590436806-1478149590438432.doc" target="CMSFILEINCONTENT">《四川大学自力志东奖学金申请表》</a></font></span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: Arial; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt">\n      <o:p></o:p></span></p>\n    <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: \'yes\'; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'">\n      <o:p>\n       &nbsp;\n      </o:p></span></p>\n    <!--EndFragment-->\n    <div id="网站群管理"></div>\n   </div></td>\n </tr>\n</tbody>', 'time': '2016-11-22T07:04:00Z', 'title': '四川大学自力志东奖学金评选通知', 'academy': '计算机学院', 'originURL': 'http://cs.scu.edu.cn/cs/xytz/webinfo/2016/11/1478149590436806.htm'}